data.description: ASSUMABLE 3.75 LOAN FOR QUALIFIED BUYERS!!  This beautiful home was the original model home when the quads were constructed.  55+ community with pool, golf course and sidewalks for strolling. Great natural lighting with large windows, 10ft. trayed ceilings and open floor plan.  Unique features include 2 suites, walk in shower, bamboo and tile flooring, westward facing porch for viewing beautiful sunsets, extra mature trees, walk in shower, corner lot, two car garage and walk up attic is plumbed so you can easily finish it out as a bonus room with a full bath.  Enjoy the tile backsplash in the kitchen and cozy gas fireplace in the winter.  Office features enhance lighting for your crafting or painting.  Street light and fire hydrant right out front.  Don't miss this one!  Prime location in gated 55+ community.
